msgid "Bridge"
msgstr "橋接"

msgid "Channel Sets"
msgstr "頻道集"

msgid "Data Channels"
msgstr "資料頻道"

msgid "Define data channels over which outbound filtered packets will flow."
msgstr "定義出站過濾封包將流經的數據通道。"

msgid ""
"Define filter rules to apply to outbound packets. Matching packets will flow "
"over the data channel."
msgstr "定義過濾規則以應用於出站封包。匹配的封包將流經數據通道。"

msgid "Define primary channels and their corresponding data channels."
msgstr "定義主頻道及其相關的資料頻道。"

msgid "Destination port"
msgstr "目的通訊埠"

msgid "Dual Channel Wi-Fi AP Daemon"
msgstr "雙頻 Wi-Fi AP 守護行程"

msgid "Dual Channel WiFi"
msgstr "雙頻 Wi-Fi"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "啟用"

msgid "Filter Sets"
msgstr "篩選器集"

msgid "Filters"
msgstr "篩選器"

msgid "General"
msgstr "一般"

msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "一般設定"

msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-dcwapd"
msgstr "授予 luci-app-dcwapd 擁有 UCI 存取的權限"

msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "介面"

msgid "MAC Address"
msgstr "MAC 位址"

msgid "Packet size"
msgstr "封包大小"

msgid "Protocol"
msgstr "協定"

msgid "SSID"
msgstr "SSID"

msgid "Select filters to apply to matching MAC addresses."
msgstr "選擇篩選器，以適用於匹配 MAC 位址。"

msgid "Source IP"
msgstr "來源 IP"

msgid "Source port"
msgstr "來源埠"

msgid "Specify the temporary directory for dcwapd file storage."
msgstr "指定 dcwapd 檔案儲存的臨時目錄。"

msgid "Temp Directory"
msgstr "臨時目錄"

msgid ""
"With %s you can use two simultaneous Wi-Fi connections to decrease wireless "
"traffic congestion and increase throughput."
msgstr ""
"通過 %s 您可以同時使用兩個 Wi-Fi 連接，以減少無線流量壅塞並提高吞吐量。"
